txt.en: You found this collar upon one of the wild cats that roam the Brown Lands. Its intricate design is unlike any you have seen before.\n\nRegardless, it is a sign that the cats are not native to the region. Twiga will want to know of this.
'Alas, you are correct, I fear. These wild cats are not at all wild. They have been trained in the art of war.\n\n'This collar is of Easterling design, and no doubt belongs to the Khundolar.'
You found a collar upon one of the wild cats of the Brown Lands. The intricate designs are not familiar to you.
Bring the collar you found to Twiga at Etheburg in the Brown Lands
Twiga is at Etheburg in the Brown Lands.\n\nYou should bring this collar to Twiga at once.
